Step 1: Start
Step 2: Declare an array and left, right, mid variable 
Step 3: Perform merge function.
        mergesort(array,left,right)
        mergesort (array, left, right)
        if left > right
        return
        mid= (left+right)/2
        mergesort(array, left, mid)
        mergesort(array, mid+1, right)
        merge(array, left, mid, right)
Step 4: Stop
